---
title: Roast Duck & Peppered Red Wine Jus with Thyme-Roasted Potatoes & Sautéed Almond Veggies
description: Pep up your roast duck with a peppery red wine jus and a side of thyme-roasted potatoes. No roast duck dish is complete without
some veggies, especially when there are almonds scattered throughout. It’s a duck feast that everyone is going to love!
